      <data key="d3">paper-01:chunk_0007</data>
      <data key="d4">method</data>
      <data key="d5">These summaries are valuable, but a method- or domain-centered perspective can obscure the deeper question driving the field: which equations can actually be discovered from the available data, and what makes them scientifically meaningful?</data>
