      <data key="d5">In parallel, Kolmogorov–Arnold Networks (KANs)51 have also been explored for PDE discovery, with KAN-ODEs52 and optPDE53 demonstrating the ability to learn hidden dynamics and identify ODE/PDE forms from sparse or noisy datasets.</data>
