      <data key="d3">paper-07:chunk_0008</data>
      <data key="d4">method</data>
      <data key="d5">Second, in our main empirical pipeline, we examine the impact of probe density, SS regression, and parcel space on within- subject classification in two HD motor-activation datasets, establishing a baseline to quantify how effec- tively our methods can improve accuracy.</data>
