      <data key="d3">paper_06:chunk_0027</data>
      <data key="d4">future_work</data>
      <data key="d5">5 Conclusions and Future Works In this work, we present SciGPT, a domain-specific large language model tailored for scientific litera- ture understanding and knowledge discovery, along with a comprehensive evaluation of its performance on ScienceBench.</data>
