    <node id="statement:stmt_54f7528f3d9d">
      <data key="d0">statement</data>
      <data key="d2">stmt_54f7528f3d9d</data>
      <data key="d1">paper_06</data>
      <data key="d3">paper_06:chunk_0027</data>
      <data key="d4">result</data>
      <data key="d5">Through a structured training pipeline encompassing domain-adapted pretraining, supervised fine-tuning (SFT), and direct preference optimization (DPO), with the architectural opti- mizations based on the Qwen3 framework, SciGPT achieves superior performance in scientific domain tasks.</data>
      <data key="d6">Through a structured training pipeline encompassing domain-adapted pretraining, supervised fine-tuning (SFT), and direct preference optimization (DPO), with the architectural opti- mizations based on the Qwen3 framework, SciGPT achieves superior performance in scientific domain tasks.</data>
      <data key="d7">rule:achieves</data>
      <data key="d8">4</data>
    </node>
