      <data key="d1">paper_06</data>
      <data key="d3">paper_06:chunk_0028</data>
      <data key="d4">result</data>
      <data key="d5">Evaluation results show that SciGPT outperforms general-purpose models like GPT-4 across multiple core tasks in the scientific domain, particularly in sequence labeling tasks such as named entity recognition and relation extraction, as well as in cross-lingual scientific text translation.</data>
      <data key="d6">Evaluation results show that SciGPT outperforms general-purpose models like GPT-4 across multiple core tasks in the scientific domain, particularly in sequence labeling tasks such as named entity recognition and relation extraction, as well as in cross-lingual scientific text translation.</data>
      <data key="d7">rule:results show</data>
      <data key="d8">1</data>
    </node>
